{"analytics_identifier":"OT564","base_path":"/government/organisations/bona-vacantia","content_id":"c9109663-0128-4db4-b513-a9cdfb691034","description":"‘Bona Vacantia’ means vacant goods and is the name given to ownerless property, which by law passes to the Crown. The Treasury Solicitor acts for the Crown to administer the estates of people who die intestate (without a Will) and without known kin (entitled blood relatives) and collect the assets of dissolved companies and other various ownerless goods in England and Wales. BVD is part of the Government Legal Department .","details":{"acronym":"BVD","alternative_format_contact_email":"bvinfo@governmentlegal.gov.uk","body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>‘Bona Vacantia’ means vacant goods and is the name given to ownerless property, which by law passes to the Crown.</p>\n\n<p>The Treasury Solicitor acts for the Crown to administer the estates of people who die intestate (without a Will) and without known kin (entitled blood relatives) and collect the assets of dissolved companies and other various ownerless goods in England and Wales.</p>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Bona Vacantia\">BVD</abbr> is part of the <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/government-legal-department\">Government Legal Department</a>.</p>\n</div>","brand":"attorney-generals-office","foi_exempt":false,"logo":{"crest":"single-identity","formatted_title":"Bona Vacantia"},"ordered_corporate_information_pages":[{"href":"/government/organisations/bona-vacantia/about/complaints-procedure","title":"Complaints procedure"}],"ordered_featured_documents":[{"document_type":"News story","href":"/government/news/temporary-closure-of-bona-vacantia-telephone-lines","image":{"alt_text":"Telephony logo 2","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69a169d6ec82ce45f05bd6ce/s712_Telephony_Logo_2.PNG","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69a169d6286b6fdc85daea98/s465_Telephony_Logo_2.PNG","url":"